- Root cause component: node-5
- Root cause occurrence timestamp: 1647768600 (2022-03-20 17:30:00+08)
- Root cause reason: node disk I/O saturation (high disk I/O consumption causing elevated system.cpu.iowait and large I/O queue length — i.e., node disk read I/O consumption/backlog), which caused service latency spikes (observed in frontend→adservice traces) and frontend errors.

